To find the $\goldE{\text{total}}$ number of spells Anna's wand can cast, we start with the number of spells $\blueE{\text{Elsa's wand}}$ can cast, and add the number of $\maroonD{\text{fewer spells}}$ Elsa's wand casts.

![](web+graphie:${☣ LOCALPATH}/images/a5f3ffda2047474fa78b0480d597c0db2782b032)

$\begin{align}
\blueE{\text{Elsa's wand}} + \maroonD{17}  &= \goldE{\text{Anna's spells}} \\\\
\blueE{53} + \maroonD{17} &= \goldE{\Box}
\end{align}$
